```json
{
  "application": "SLURM",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "bcftools",
      "tabix",
      "awk",
      "conda"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "memory": "16G",
      "disk": "512G",
      "time": "12:00:00",
      "environment": "gwas",
      "dependencies": [
        "gwaslab"
      ]
    },
    "input": [
      "/hpc/dhl_ec/data/references/1000G/Phase3/VCF_format/ALL.chr*.phase3_shapeit2_mvncall_integrated_v5a.20130502.genotypes.vcf.gz",
      "/hpc/dhl_ec/data/references/1000G/Phase3/integrated_call_samples_v3.20130502.ALL.panel",
      "/hpc/dhl_ec/data/references/1000G/human_g1k_v37.fasta"
    ],
    "output": [
      "/hpc/dhl_ec/data/references/1000G/Phase3/VCF_format/*.split_norm_af.vcf.gz",
      "/hpc/dhl_ec/data/references/1000G/Phase3/VCF_format/*.concat_list.txt"
    ],
    "notes": [
      "This script is designed to run on a SLURM cluster",
      "It uses the 'gwas' conda environment",
      "The script processes reference data for harmonization/normalization of GWAS data with GWASLab",
      "It extracts sample lists for different populations",
      "It splits, normalizes, and merges VCF files for each population",
      "It uses temporary disk space of 512G",
      "It requires 16G of memory",
      "It is expected to run for 12 hours"
    ]
  }
}
```
